%%{init: {"sequence": {"messageMargin": 64, "noteMargin": 24, "boxMargin": 18, "wrap": true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Authenticated Voter
    participant App as Voting App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database
    participant Hub as Official Realtime Hub

    Note over User,App: Starts after successful result from voter-auth-dataflow-only

    App->>Server: GET /api/candidates
    Server-->>App: Candidate list
    App-->>User: Show ballot paper

    User->>App: Select candidate and confirm vote
    App->>Server: POST /api/voter/cast-vote
    Server->>Server: Validate token claims (voter, station, constituency)
    Server->>DB: Check voter has not already voted
    Server->>DB: Verify candidate and polling station
    DB-->>Server: Validation result

    alt Valid vote
        Server->>DB: Mark voter HasVoted = true
        Server->>DB: Insert vote record
        Server->>Hub: Notify linked official(s) via SignalR
        Server-->>App: 200 vote successfully cast
        App-->>User: Show vote confirmed
    else Already voted or invalid context
        Server-->>App: 400 vote failed
        App-->>User: Show error and request official help
    end
